e photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Jocelyne De Nicola"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/jocelyne-de-nicola/">View all articles by Jocelyne De Nicola</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/10/trieste-teatro-verdistabat-mater/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Trieste, Teatro Verdi:&#8221;Stabat Mater&#8221;</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/10/yuri-temirkanov-interpreta-cajkovskij-e-musorgskij-alla-fenice/" rel="next">Yuri Temirkanov interpreta ajkovskij e Musorgskij alla Fenice <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2012/10/toulouse-theatre-du-capitolerienzi/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sar pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="required">*</span></p><p class="comment-form-comment"><label for="comment">Commento</label><textarea id="comment" name="comment" cols="45" rows="8" maxlength="65525" aria-required="true" required="required"></textarea></p><p class="comment-form-author"><label for="author">Nome <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="author" name="author" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="245" aria-required=\'true\' required=\'required\' /></p><p class="comment-form-email"><label for="email">Email <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="email" name="email" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="100" aria-describedby="email-notes" aria-required=\'true\' required=\'required\' /></p><p class="comment-form-url"><label for="url">Sito web</label> <input id="url" name="url" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="200" /></p><p class="form-submit"><input name="submit" type="submit" id="submit" class="submit" value="Commento all&#039;articolo" /> <input type=\'hidden\' name=\'comment_post_ID\' value=\'41631\' id=\'comment_post_ID\' /> <input type=\'hidden\' name=\'comment_parent\' id=\'comment_parent\' value=\'0\' /></p><p style="display: none;"><input type="hidden" id="akismet_comment_nonce" name="akismet_comment_nonce" value="9fda8d9f14" /></p><p style="display: none;"><input type="hidden" id="ak_js" name="ak_js" value="162"/></p></form></div></div></div></div></div><div id="secondary" class="widget-area span4 sb-4" role="complementary"> <aside id="search-4" class="widget widget_search clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">RICERCA</h3><form method="get" id="searchform" action="http://www.gbopera.it/"> <label for="s" class="assistive-text">Search</label> <input type="text" class="field" name="s" id="s" placeholder="Search" /> <button type="submit" class="submit btn" name="submit" id="searchsubmit"><i class="icon-search"></i></button></form> </aside><aside id="ct-relatedposts-widget-2" class="widget ct-relatedposts-widget clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">Articoli correlati</h3><ul class="related-posts-single clearfix"><li> <a href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/martina-franca-42-festival-della-valle-ditria-la-grotta-di-trofonio/\' title=\'Martina Franca, 42 Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;\'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="la grotta di Trofonio, Martina Franca 2016" title="Martina Franca, 42 Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/opera-di-firenze-cortile-di-palazzo-pitti-la-traviata/\' title=\'Opera di Firenze, Cortile di Palazzo Pitti: &#8220;La Traviata&#8221;\'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/La-traviata-prima-Simone-Donati-TerraProject-Contrasto-10-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="La traviata (prima) Simone Donati - TerraProject - Contrasto (10)" title="Opera di Firenze, Cortile di Palazzo Pitti: &#8220;La Traviata&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/La-traviata-prima-Simone-Donati-TerraProject-Contrasto-10-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/La-traviata-prima-Simone-Donati-TerraProject-Contrasto-10-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/i-puritani-al-teatro-real-di-madrid/\' title=\'I Puritani al Teatro Real di Madrid\'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-11-VII-2016-I-Puritani-8-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Madrid, Teatro Real, 11 VII 2016 (I Puritani) 8" title="I Puritani al Teatro Real di Madrid" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-11-VII-2016-I-Puritani-8-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-11-VII-2016-I-Puritani-8-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/roma-terme-di-caracalla-stagione-lirica-2016-nabucco/\' title=\'Roma, Terme di Caracalla, Stagione Lirica 2016: &#8220;Nabucco&#8221;\'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Nabucco_Il-coro-nel-Va-pensiero_Yasuko-Kageyama-Opera-di-Roma-Caracalla-2016_7566-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Nabucco_Il coro nel Va pensiero_Yasuko Kageyama-Opera di Roma, Caracalla 2016_7566" title="Roma, Terme di Caracalla, Stagione Lirica 2016: &#8220;Nabucco&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Nabucco_Il-coro-nel-Va-pensiero_Yasuko-Kageyama-Opera-di-Roma-Caracalla-2016_7566-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Nabucco_Il-coro-nel-Va-pensiero_Yasuko-Kageyama-Opera-di-Roma-Caracalla-2016_7566-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/staatsoper-stuttgart-i-puritani/\' title=\'Staatsoper Stuttgart: &#8220;I Puritani&#8221;\'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/41852_puritani__hpo_33-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="puritani, stuttgart, 2016" title="Staatsoper Stuttgart: &#8220;I Puritani&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/41852_puritani__hpo_33-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/41852_puritani__hpo_33-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/milano-teatro-alla-scala-simon-boccanegra-cast-alternativo/\' title=\'Milano, Teatro alla Scala: &#8220;Simon Boccanegra&#8221; (cast alternativo)\'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/scala-boccanegra-3-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="scala-boccanegra-3" title="Milano, Teatro alla Scala: &#8220;Simon Boccanegra&#8221; (cast alternativo)" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/scala-boccanegra-3-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/scala-boccanegra-3-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li></ul> </aside></div></div></div><div id="footer" role="contentinfo"><div class="container"><div class="row-fluid"><div class="span6"><div class="copyright-info"> Associazione Culturale GB Opera<br/>Sede legale: vicolo Scala Santa 6 - 37129 Verona<br/>Codice fiscale: 93238110238 - info@gbopera.it<br/> Pubblicazione ai sensi della legge n. 62 del 07.03.2001.<br/>Copyright  2008-2016</div></div><div class="span6"><div class="add-info"></div></div></div></div></div><script type="text/javascript">jQuery.noConflict()(function($){$(document).ready(function(){var $container=$(\'#blog-entry\');$container.imagesLoaded(function(){$container.masonry({itemSelector:\'.masonry-box\',isAnimated:true,});});});});</script><script type="text/javascript">jQuery(document).ready(function(){var q2w3_sidebar_1_options={"sidebar":"q2w3-default-sidebar","margin_top":0,"margin_bottom":0,"stop_id":"","screen_max_width":0,"width_inherit":false,"widgets":[\'mainmenu-block-bg\']};q2w3_sidebar(q2w3_sidebar_1_options);setInterval(function(){q2w3_sidebar(q2w3_sidebar_1_options);},1500);});</script><script type=\'text/javascript\' src=\'http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/plugins/akismet/_inc/form.js\'></script><script type=\'text/javascript\'>var ajax_var={"url":"http:\\/\\/www.gbopera.it\\/wp-admin\\/admin-ajax.php","nonce":"b11bd15afa"};</script><script type=\'text/javascript\'>var ct_localization={"go_to":"MENU","to_top":"To the Top","no_posts":"No more posts to load."};</script><script type=\'text/javascript\' src=\'http://www.gbopera.it/wp-includes/js/wp-embed.js\'></script><scri